overview: Emotionally Exhausting shows why Liz Miele is a favorite from the New York scene. With a sharp mind, she takes on a wide range of topics that flow together seamlessly. This show can double as a blueprint for channeling personal insecurities and anxieties into positive energy. Not many people can laugh about having a cat that interrupts your sex life.
title: Liz Miele: Emotionally Exhausting
